        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nBuild Failed \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/policy-gui-sonar/402/ : FAILURE (skipped)\n\nSyntax error in markdown file ( https://jenkins.onap.org/job/policy-gui-sonar/402/ )\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/policy-gui-sonar/402",
